# NOTE: This file is NOT auto-honored by GitHub Pages + Cloudflare CDN.
#
# It's kept here as:
# 1. Documentation of intended MIME types for AI infra files
# 2. Reference for future Cloudflare Pages migration (CF Pages honors _headers)
# 3. Spec for the equivalent Cloudflare Transform Rule that should be deployed
#    at zone level (see Cloudflare → Rules → Transform Rules → "Modify Response Header")
#
# Current state (2026-05-11):
# - GitHub Pages serves /.well-known/ai.txt + /llms.txt as text/plain by default
# - Most AI parsers (Anthropic, Perplexity, OpenAI) accept text/plain llms.txt
# - text/markdown Content-Type would be marginally better for llms.txt but
#   not blocking for current AI agent compat
#
# To deploy these headers via Cloudflare Transform Rule, create a rule with:
#   When:  http.request.uri.path eq "/llms.txt"
#   Then:  Set static Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=utf-8
#
# Repeat per path. Or wait until Cloudflare Pages migration if planned.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# /llms.txt — AI agent navigation index (Markdown format)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
/llms.txt
  Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# /.well-known/ai.txt — AI permissions manifest (plain text)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
/.well-known/ai.txt
  Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# /.well-known/security.txt — RFC 9116 (plain text)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
/.well-known/security.txt
  Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# /robots.txt — plain text (override default)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
/robots.txt
  Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
